snippet.title: Kanon Intro (Game Opening)
snippet.description:
Intro of the legendary good ren'ai VN "Kanon" by Key/Visual Art's from 1999 on Playstation 2.

Play it! (Or watch it @Kanon 2006 ;) )

Song: Ayana - Last Regrets
